➜广东诗人小隐：天净沙.立冬
http://www.sohu.com/a/430437674_100115135	47680
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201108/8579bd2fe0104d8b851a0fe209bd648a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>天净沙.立冬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高楼百尺人家，色青云淡窗花。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却是谁人误画？斜阳西下，有心追梦天涯。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201108/5045c0fb070a42fab39c21a6759d476b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>小隐，自由职业者，一个游走人间的过客，喜欢用文字与灵魂对话的小女人，左手柴米油盐酱拌醋～右手诗词歌赋花间茶～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201108/a59f9b457d9d41648e0802b3a056851b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
