➜河南诗人王琦伟：七绝·立冬（二首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/430438651_100115135	48163
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201108/ecfed1b1d95c45cd93836d6d9e2da482.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·立冬（平水韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/梦回桃花源（王琦伟）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">初享天伦乐已痴，春风满面逸馨时。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今朝父爱儿欢笑，他日家兴自雅诗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020·11·7</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201108/8208c2e1f893464483b29602f79fcf0e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">﻿</span></strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·立冬（中华新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/梦回桃花源（王琦伟）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">悄去秋妆暖日融，溧园月季蕊香浓。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">若无枯叶随风舞，恰似阳春未立冬。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
