➜广西诗人陈熠明：长空万里梦云飞
http://www.sohu.com/a/430440038_100115135	48953
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201108/aa67175e9e184200a07d54f292c5bb52.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>长空万里梦云飞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·长空万里梦云飞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逍遥浪漫清风远，四海丹霞日影陪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">过往来回方远去，长空万里梦云飞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·无边只爱任随飘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流连忘返问清高，自醉长空万里遥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不羡缠绵伤海痛，无边只爱任随飘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(三)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·风流雨泪化愁浓</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日上云霞飞浪漫，风流雨泪化愁浓。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥心不恋红尘客，笑看朝夕梦远空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201108/b68df39b97f74288aa63666498063146.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(四)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·逍遥看罢世间经</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫笑飞花顺水情，逍遥看罢世间经，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘游四海风流远，自醉云霞万里行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(五)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·淡忘伤情烟往事</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">愁心落远天涯客，梦里相逢又是秋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">淡忘伤情烟往事，云霞伴我笑风流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(六)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·自醉飘来上远高</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清杯不问日边潮，自醉飘来上远高。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笑换别情伤眼泪，长天万里尽逍遥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201108/9ddb7180860f402b86bdaf4582943a74.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(七)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·梦在云中自远高</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">静水流深别岁月，清风四海荡逍遥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平生一路尘前客，梦在云中自远高。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(八)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·别经落泪痛尘缘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">世事无常梦雨烟，别经落泪痛尘缘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘来不问将何去，伴我云霞静水天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(九)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·浩瀚胸怀荡远清</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长风破浪飞云海，浩瀚胸怀荡远清。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远上无涯流过客，逍遥自在碧天行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201108/dd20731fb64e433faa8e826a5fe36309.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·心随四海笑春华</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心随四海笑春华，广阔长天处处家。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫叹流年风雨路，回头便是美云霞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·重逢万里青云外</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荡去乘风沧海浪，长空望远笑君临。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重逢万里青云外，日上高天自在心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·自在长天梦远鹰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日影江花笑水清，云飞过往动黎明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翱翔展翅凌空上，自在长天梦远鹰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201108/9f99e3b1caf84d90b63e5edcfecc825f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>陈熠明，笔名心灵诗幻，男，1976年生，广西平果市人。爱好文学创作，曾有诗歌作品发布于多家报刊杂志和网络。时任星连文学社副社长。职业于中医，热衷于传统文化传播。诗是文笔与文笔的向往，诗是朋友与朋友的交心。诗是千难和万险的将来，诗是岁月与年华的渴望。诗是春夏和秋冬的风景，诗是父亲和母亲的嘱咐，诗是父亲和母亲的叮咛。诗是渡船与碧波的远航，诗是生命与大海的彼岸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201108/4d282f36fe62439695e6f577e7c352c4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
